{"tid":516694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警偕女友人店舖狂盜　人贓並獲被捕","createTime":"2018-01-01T15:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T17:18:24.000Z","uid":53379,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7557ce9ab06f299c80091d928838b95a80f3d8","tid":516694,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">休班警偕女友人店舖狂盜　人贓並獲被捕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n再有警務人員涉嫌「知法犯法」。一名休班警員昨日除夕與女友人在尖沙嘴The One商場一間內超市內偷去12件總值460元貨品，被商場保安員現截查「人贓並獲」報警。<br />\n<br />\n被捕兩人分別為23歲姓羅男子及22歲姓仇女子。羅為休班警員，兩人涉嫌盜竊罪名，暫准保釋候查，須於本月上旬返警署報到。案件交由油尖警區重案組第1隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n現場為尖沙嘴彌敦道100號The One商場。消息稱，昨午4時許，當時羅與仇女在The One商場Aeon超級市場內遊逛，其間接連將12件共值460元貨品藏到所攜袋內，未有付款就離去。商場63歲姓鍾保安員目擊過程，截停兩人搜查檢獲有關貨品，隨即報警召警員到場，並以相關罪名拘捕兩人帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180101/s00001/1514820106717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180101%2Fs00001%2F1514820106717&d=%2FDaPASuomOV0xQYjFkgKh8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f3e9436d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180101%2Fs00001%2F1514820106717&h=e1273db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180101/s00001/1514820106717</a>"},{"pid":"e62e82e02ad2f9de6aca3bf7463b18eadc8cab90","tid":516694,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"姓仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe97b60076ca272719668e6e53264fb969542d7","tid":516694,"uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"2626c09b7f2c05e9c3b8c88edf7921152f6d6b6f","tid":516694,"uid":22087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"果幾舊水野都要偷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef330bd17f4d1cde0c6305b2c58d692c096aee0a","tid":516694,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"警方發言人表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n有幾多真係會紀律聆訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23be5f6b49d6670f52c0579ca007ab657180829","tid":516694,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中啦"},{"pid":"8ef18557cb7d0dd9dc220a63debb666a9ad23306","tid":516694,"uid":159775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"最大犯罪團體 休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3212af563e538f55db80e03ea9844d68a2d08a25","tid":516694,"uid":72396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"睇黎我識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c79047345ae1a299557658a7c72ca49e7e55b5c","tid":516694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3212af563e538f55db80e03ea9844d68a2d08a25","tid":516694,"uid":72396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"睇黎我識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5b8bd732a63c44d9048c2b8e1fa5e7fd4e6bbc","tid":516694,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"新年第一日 <br />\n全取三分"}]}